                                                                                        VertexType start,
                                                                                        VertexType end,
                                                                                        java.util.List<VertexType> vertexList,
                                                                                        java.util.List<EdgeType> edgeList)
        Function for generating a simple Path. The given information are being checked against the given Graph.
        Type Parameters:
        VertexType - the type of vertex being used inside the Path.
        EdgeType - the type of Edge being used to connect all vertices inside the Path.
        Parameters:
        graph - the Graph the information are being checked against.
        start - the starting vertex of the Path.
        end - the end vertex of the Path.
        vertexList - the List of all vertices of the Path. These elements also get checked to secure their conformity with the given Graph.
        edgeList - the List of all edges of the Path. These elements also get checked to secure their conformity with the given Graph.
        Returns:
        a Path leading from one point inside the Graph to another one.
